# Retail Store Sales Analysis (Python EDA)

## Project Overview

This project performs **Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)** on a retail store dataset containing **11,971 transactions**.
The goal was to clean the dataset, analyze purchasing behavior, and visualize key business insights.

The analysis was performed using **Python, pandas, and matplotlib** in a Jupyter Notebook environment.

---

## Dataset Information

The dataset includes transaction-level retail data with the following fields:

* Transaction_ID
* Customer_ID
* Category
* Item
* Price_Per_Unit
* Quantity
* Total_Spent
* Payment_Method
* Location (Online / In-store)
* Transaction_Date

Total records analyzed: **11,971 transactions**

---

## Tools & Technologies

* Python
* Pandas (Data Cleaning & Analysis)
* Matplotlib (Data Visualization)
* Jupyter Notebook

